  - name: FACILITYHEADSURVEY_DICT.Q1_NAME
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>We would like to ask some of your personal information relevant to the survey.</p><p>1. What is your name? (Last Name, First Name, Middle Initial, Ext)</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>We would like to ask some of your personal information relevant to the survey.</p><p>Ano ang iyong pangalan? (Last Name, First Name, Middle Initial, Ext)</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>We would like to ask some of your personal information relevant to the survey.</p><p>Ano an saimong Pangaran? (Apelyido, Ngaran, Middle Initial, Ext)</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>We would like to ask some of your personal information relevant to the survey.</p><p>Unsa ang imohang pangalan (Apelyido, Unang Pangalan, apelyido sa Mama sa pagkadalaga, Ext.)</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>We would like to ask some of your personal information relevant to the survey.</p><p>Unsa imong pangalan? (Apelyido, Pangalan, Middle Initial, EXT</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>We would like to ask some of your personal information relevant to the survey.</p><p>Ano it imo ngaran? (Apelyido, Siyahan nga ngaran, Butnga, Dugang ha ngaran)</p>
          HIL: |
            <p>We would like to ask some of your personal information relevant to the survey.</p><p>Ano ang imo ngalan? (Last Name, First Name, Middle Initial, Ext)</p>
  - name: FACILITYHEADSURVEY_DICT.Q2_FACILITY_ROLE
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>2. What is your official designation at this health facility?</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Ano ang iyong responsibilidad na ginagampanan sa pasilidad na ito?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>2. What is your official designation at this health facility?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>2. What is your official designation at this health facility?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Unsa imong posisyon/papel dinhi sa health facility?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Ano an imo opisyal nga designasyon hini nga pasilidad panlawas?</p>
          HIL: |
            <p>Ano ang imo opisyal nga katungdanan sa ini nga health facility?</p>
  - name: FACILITYHEADSURVEY_DICT.Q3_AGE
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>3. How old are you (in years), as of your last birthday?</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Ilang taon ka na noong huling kaarawan mo?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Pira an edad mo (sa taon), base sa huring kompleanyo mo?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Pilay edad nimo base sa imohang nga adlawng natawhan?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Pila na imong edad (sa tuig) base sa imong miaging birthday?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Pir an an imo edad tikang han imo urhi nga kaadlawa? (ha mga tuig)</p>
