          EN: |
            <p>We will now ask about your awareness of UHC, the changes that have been implemented in this facility since the UHC Act was passed in 2019 and if these changes were a result of the UHC Act.</p><p>9. Have you heard about Universal Health Care (UHC) prior to this survey?</p>
