            <p>We will now ask about your awareness of UHC, the changes that have been implemented in this facility since the UHC Act was passed in 2019 and if these changes were a result of the UHC Act.</p><p>Sa wala pa ning survey, naka dungog na ba ka ug impormasyon kabahin sa Universal Health Care (UHC)?</p>
          CEB: |
