  - name: FACILITYHEADSURVEY_DICT.Q12_PCB_LICENSING
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>12. Has the facility applied for DOH primary care licensing since the UHC Act was passed in 2019 and was it a result of the UHC Act?</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. USE THE FOLLOWING GUIDE QUESTIONS TO PROBE. Has this been implemented? / Do you have this? Was this implemented before or after 2019? Was this implemented because of UHC? Do you plan to implement it in the next 1-2 years?</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Ang pasilidad ba ay nag-apply para sa DOH primary care licensing mula nang maipasa ang UHC Act noong 2019, at ito ba ay bunga ng UHC Act?</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. USE THE FOLLOWING GUIDE QUESTIONS TO PROBE. Has this been implemented? / Do you have this? Was this implemented before or after 2019? Was this implemented because of UHC? Do you plan to implement it in the next 1-2 years?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Nag apply na an pasilidad na ini para sa Lisensya sa DOH Primary care poon kan naipasa an UHC Act kan 2019, asin resulta daw ini kan UHC Act?</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. USE THE FOLLOWING GUIDE QUESTIONS TO PROBE. Has this been implemented? / Do you have this? Was this implemented before or after 2019? Was this implemented because of UHC? Do you plan to implement it in the next 1-2 years?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Ang pasilidad ba ni-apply og lisensya sa primary care sukad gipasa ang UHC Act niadtong 2019, resulta ba kini sa maong balaod?</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. USE THE FOLLOWING GUIDE QUESTIONS TO PROBE. Has this been implemented? / Do you have this? Was this implemented before or after 2019? Was this implemented because of UHC? Do you plan to implement it in the next 1-2 years?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Ni apply ba ang pasilidad para sa DOH licensing sukad napasar ang UHC Act in 2019 ug resulta ba kini sa UHC Act?</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. USE THE FOLLOWING GUIDE QUESTIONS TO PROBE. Has this been implemented? / Do you have this? Was this implemented before or after 2019? Was this implemented because of UHC? Do you plan to implement it in the next 1-2 years?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Nag-apply na ba an pasilidad hin DOH primary care licensing tikang han pagpasa han UHC Act hadton 2019 ngan resulta ba ini han UHC Act?</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. USE THE FOLLOWING GUIDE QUESTIONS TO PROBE. Has this been implemented? / Do you have this? Was this implemented before or after 2019? Was this implemented because of UHC? Do you plan to implement it in the next 1-2 years?</p>
          HIL: |
            <p>Nag-apply bala ang ospital sang DOH primary care licensing umpisa nga ginpasar ang UHC Act sang 2019 ukon resulta ini sang UHC Act?</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. USE THE FOLLOWING GUIDE QUESTIONS TO PROBE. Has this been implemented? / Do you have this? Was this implemented before or after 2019? Was this implemented because of UHC? Do you plan to implement it in the next 1-2 years?</p>
