    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>14. If yes, has the creation of a public health unit at this facility been implemented since the UHC Act was passed in 2019 and was it a result of the UHC Act?</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. USE THE FOLLOWING GUIDE QUESTIONS TO PROBE. Has this been implemented? / Do you have this? Was this implemented before or after 2019? Was this implemented because of UHC? Do you plan to implement it in the next 1-2 years?</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Kung oo, naipatupad na ba ang pagtatayo ng public health unit sa pasilidad na ito mula nang maipasa ang UHC Act noong 2019, at ito ba ay bunga ng pagpapatupad ng UHC Act?</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. USE THE FOLLOWING GUIDE QUESTIONS TO PROBE. Has this been implemented? / Do you have this? Was this implemented before or after 2019? Was this implemented because of UHC? Do you plan to implement it in the next 1-2 years?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Kun “iyo”, an paggibo pa kan Public Health Unit digdi sa pasilidad na ini naipatupad ba daw hale kan naipasa an UHC Act kan 2019, asin resulta ba daw ini kan UHC Act?</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. USE THE FOLLOWING GUIDE QUESTIONS TO PROBE. Has this been implemented? / Do you have this? Was this implemented before or after 2019? Was this implemented because of UHC? Do you plan to implement it in the next 1-2 years?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Kung oo, ang paghimo sa public health unit nahitabo ba sukad sa pagpasa sa UHC Act niadtong 2019? O resulta kini sa UHC Act mismo?</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. USE THE FOLLOWING GUIDE QUESTIONS TO PROBE. Has this been implemented? / Do you have this? Was this implemented before or after 2019? Was this implemented because of UHC? Do you plan to implement it in the next 1-2 years?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Kung Oo, ang paghimo ba sa public health unit niini nga pasilidad gipatuman sukad nga napasar ang UHC Act sa 2019 ug resulta ba kini sa UHC Act?</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. USE THE FOLLOWING GUIDE QUESTIONS TO PROBE. Has this been implemented? / Do you have this? Was this implemented before or after 2019? Was this implemented because of UHC? Do you plan to implement it in the next 1-2 years?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Kun oo, naimplementar na ba an paghimo hin public health unit hini nga pasilidad tikang han pagpasa han UHC Act hadton 2019 ngan resulta ba ini han UHC Act?</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. USE THE FOLLOWING GUIDE QUESTIONS TO PROBE. Has this been implemented? / Do you have this? Was this implemented before or after 2019? Was this implemented because of UHC? Do you plan to implement it in the next 1-2 years?</p>
          HIL: |
            <p>Kun huo, ang public health unit sa ini nga pasilidad ginhimo matapos ginpasar ang UHC Act sang 2019 kag resulta ini sang UHC Act?</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. USE THE FOLLOWING GUIDE QUESTIONS TO PROBE. Has this been implemented? / Do you have this? Was this implemented before or after 2019? Was this implemented because of UHC? Do you plan to implement it in the next 1-2 years?</p>
