  - name: FACILITYHEADSURVEY_DICT.Q17_HPU_CREATED
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>17. If yes, has the creation of a health promotion unit at this facility been implemented since the UHC Act was passed in 2019 and was it a result of the UHC Act?</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. USE THE FOLLOWING GUIDE QUESTIONS TO PROBE. Has this been implemented? / Do you have this? Was this implemented before or after 2019? Was this implemented because of UHC? Do you plan to implement it in the next 1-2 years?</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Kung oo, naipatupad na ba ang pagtatatag ng yunit para sa promosyon ng kalusugan sa pasilidad na ito mula nang maipasa ang UHC Act noong 2019, at ito ba ay naging resulta ng UHC Act?</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. USE THE FOLLOWING GUIDE QUESTIONS TO PROBE. Has this been implemented? / Do you have this? Was this implemented before or after 2019? Was this implemented because of UHC? Do you plan to implement it in the next 1-2 years?</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Kun iyo, sa pagbuo ba kan health promotion unit sa pasilidad na ini naimplementa ba manungod sa UHC Act na naipasa kan 2019 asin resulta ini kan UHC Act?</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. USE THE FOLLOWING GUIDE QUESTIONS TO PROBE. Has this been implemented? / Do you have this? Was this implemented before or after 2019? Was this implemented because of UHC? Do you plan to implement it in the next 1-2 years?</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Kung oo, ang pahimo ba sa health promotion unit niining pasilidad nahitabo sukad na pasa ang UHC Act niadtong 2019 ug kin iba resulta sa maong balaod?</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. USE THE FOLLOWING GUIDE QUESTIONS TO PROBE. Has this been implemented? / Do you have this? Was this implemented before or after 2019? Was this implemented because of UHC? Do you plan to implement it in the next 1-2 years?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Kung Oo, ang paghimo ba sa health promotion unit niini nga pasilidad gipatuman sukad nga napasar ang UHC Act sa 2019 ug resulta ba kini sa UHC Act?</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. USE THE FOLLOWING GUIDE QUESTIONS TO PROBE. Has this been implemented? / Do you have this? Was this implemented before or after 2019? Was this implemented because of UHC? Do you plan to implement it in the next 1-2 years?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Kun oo, naimplementar na ba an paghimo hin health promotion unit hini nga pasilidad tikang han pagpasa han UHC Act hadton 2019 ngan resulta ba ini han UHC Act?</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. USE THE FOLLOWING GUIDE QUESTIONS TO PROBE. Has this been implemented? / Do you have this? Was this implemented before or after 2019? Was this implemented because of UHC? Do you plan to implement it in the next 1-2 years?</p>
          HIL: |
            <p>Kon huo, ang pagpatukod sang health promotion unit sa sini nga pasilidad ginpatuman bala umpisa sang pag-aprobar sang UHC Act sang 2019, kag ini bala resulta sang UHC Act?</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. USE THE FOLLOWING GUIDE QUESTIONS TO PROBE. Has this been implemented? / Do you have this? Was this implemented before or after 2019? Was this implemented because of UHC? Do you plan to implement it in the next 1-2 years?</p>
