            <p>Naipatupad na ba ang pagtatatag ng mga bagong tungkulin sa pasilidad mula nang maipasa ang Batas ng UHC noong 2019, at ito ba ay naging resulta ng UHC Act?</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. USE THE FOLLOWING GUIDE QUESTIONS TO PROBE. Has this been implemented? / Do you have this? Was this implemented before or after 2019? Was this implemented because of UHC? Do you plan to implement it in the next 1-2 years?</p>
          BCL: |
