            <p>Nahimo ba ang pag-establisar og bag-ong mga papel/katungdanan sa pasilidad sukad gipasa ang UHC Act kaniadtong 2019, ug kini ba resulta sa maong balaod?</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. USE THE FOLLOWING GUIDE QUESTIONS TO PROBE. Has this been implemented? / Do you have this? Was this implemented before or after 2019? Was this implemented because of UHC? Do you plan to implement it in the next 1-2 years?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Napatuman ba ang pag-establisar ug bag-ong katungdanan or departamento sa pasilidad sukad napasar ang UHC Act sa 2019 ug resulta ba kini sa UHC ACT?</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. USE THE FOLLOWING GUIDE QUESTIONS TO PROBE. Has this been implemented? / Do you have this? Was this implemented before or after 2019? Was this implemented because of UHC? Do you plan to implement it in the next 1-2 years?</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Naimplementar ba an pagbutang hin bag- nga mga posisyon o responsiblidad ha pasilidad tikang han pagpasa han UHC Act dida han 2019 ngan resulta ba ini han UHC Act?</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. USE THE FOLLOWING GUIDE QUESTIONS TO PROBE. Has this been implemented? / Do you have this? Was this implemented before or after 2019? Was this implemented because of UHC? Do you plan to implement it in the next 1-2 years?</p>
          HIL: |
            <p>Ang pag-establisar sang bag-o nga mga papel sa pasilidad ginpatuman bala umpisa sang pag-aprobar sang UHC Act sang 2019, kag ini bala resulta sang UHC Act?</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. USE THE FOLLOWING GUIDE QUESTIONS TO PROBE. Has this been implemented? / Do you have this? Was this implemented before or after 2019? Was this implemented because of UHC? Do you plan to implement it in the next 1-2 years?</p>
