            <p>32. Does your facility currently submit health and financial data to the DOH Information System and/or the PhilHealth Dashboard?</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Kasalukuyan bang nagsusumite ang inyong pasilidad ng rutinang datos sa kalusugan at pinansyal sa DOH Information System at/o sa PhilHealth Dashboard?</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p>
          BCL: |
