          BIS: |
            <p>Naga sumite ba ug health and financial data sa DOH Information System and/or Philealth Dashboard ang inyong pasilidad?</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Naga sumite ba ang inyong pasilidad ug datos sa kahimsog ug pinansyal sa DOH Information System ug/o PhilHealth Dashboard?</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p>
          WAR: |
