          HIL: |
            <p>Ang inyo pasilidad nagapasa bala sang health kag financial data sa DOH Information System kag/ukon sa PhilHealth Dashboard?</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ONE ANSWER ONLY.</p>
