  - name: FACILITYHEADSURVEY_DICT.Q49_QUALITY_CHALL_O01
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>49. What are the major challenges to improving the quality of patient care in your local area? — Limited resources (personnel, equipment, supplies, funding)</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Limitadong mapagkukunan (hal. kakulangan sa healthcare personnel/manpower, medikal na kagamitan, mahahalagang suplay, o pondo)</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Limitadong na mga resources (kakulangan sa healthcare personnel/manpower, medical na mga gamit, essential asin supplies, o kaya pondo)</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>49. What are the major challenges to improving the quality of patient care in your local area? — Limited resources (personnel, equipment, supplies, funding)</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Limitado ang resources (e.g. kulang sa health workers/tauhan, medical equipment, kinahanglanong mga supplies, o funding</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Limitado nga mga kagamitan (pananglitan, kakulang hin mga tawohan/tawo ha pag-ataman han panlawas, mga gamit medikal, mga kinahanglanon nga mga suplay, o pondo)</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          HIL: |
            <p>Kulang sa resources/rekurso (e.g., kulang sa healthcare personnel/manpower, medical equipment, essential supplies, ukon pondo)</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
