            <p>Mabudlay nga quality standards (e.g., mataas nga standards nga indi masarangan)</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
  - name: FACILITYHEADSURVEY_DICT.Q49_QUALITY_CHALL_O03
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>49. What are the major challenges to improving the quality of patient care in your local area? — Healthcare decisions made by LGUs not the facility</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Ang ilang desisyon sa pangangalaga sa kalusugan ay ginagawa ng lokal na pamahalaan at hindi ng pasilidad</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Mga desisyon ginigibo kan LGU bako kan pasilidad bako an nasa health facility</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>49. What are the major challenges to improving the quality of patient care in your local area? — Healthcare decisions made by LGUs not the facility</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Pipila ka mga desisyon sa healthcare gihimo sa lokal nga gobyerno ug dili sa health facility</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>An pipira nga mga desisyon ha pag-ataman han kahimsog ginhihimo han mga yunit han lokal nga gobyerno ngan diri han pasilidad ha kahimsog</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          HIL: |
            <p>Ang pila ka healthcare decisions ginahimo sang local government units kag indi sang health facility</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
  - name: FACILITYHEADSURVEY_DICT.Q49_QUALITY_CHALL_O04
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>49. What are the major challenges to improving the quality of patient care in your local area? — Lack of specific healthcare skills</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Kakulangan sa partikular na kasanayan sa pangangalaga sa kalusugan (hal. kulang ang mga espesyalista, surgeon, o ibang propesyonal na may espesyal na kasanayan na kailangan sa pasilidad)</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Kulang sa specific healthcare skills ( I.e., Kakulangan ki mga espesyalista, surgeons, asin iba pang healthcare professionals na igwa ki specialized skills na kaipuhan kan pasalidad)</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>49. What are the major challenges to improving the quality of patient care in your local area? — Lack of specific healthcare skills</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Kakulangan sa specific healthcare skills (I.e. dili paigo ang espesyalista, surgeon, o uban pang healthcare professionals)</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Kakulang hin partikular nga mga abilidad ha pag-ataman han panlawas (i.e., Kulang nga mga espesyalista, mga siruhano, o iba pa nga mga propesyonal ha pag-ataman han panlawas nga mayda mga espesyalista nga mga abilidad nga ginkikinahanglan ha pasilidad)</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          HIL: |
            <p>Kulang sa specific healthcare skills (e.g., kulang sa specialists, surgeons, ukon iban nga professionals nga may espesyal nga abilidad nga kinahanglanon sang pasilidad)</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
  - name: FACILITYHEADSURVEY_DICT.Q49_QUALITY_CHALL_O05
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>49. What are the major challenges to improving the quality of patient care in your local area? — Inadequate training of healthcare workers</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Hindi sapat na pagsasanay ng mga healthcare worker (hal. kailangan ng karagdagang training upang maabot ang kalidad ng pamantayan ng pasilidad)</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Daing sapat na training sa mga healthcare workers (I.e., healthcare workers kaipuhan ki dagdag na trasining para sa marhay na quality standards kan pasilidad)</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>49. What are the major challenges to improving the quality of patient care in your local area? — Inadequate training of healthcare workers</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Kakulangan ug training sa mga healthcare workers (I.e. kinahanglang ang mga dugang nga training para sa mga healthcare workers aron maka meet sa quality standard sa pasilidad)</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Kulang nga pag-aram han mga trabahador ha pag-ataman han panlawas (i.e., Mga trabahador ha pag-ataman han panlawas nga nagkikinahanglan hin kadugangan nga paghag-id para matuman an mga suruklan han kalidad han pasilidad)</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          HIL: |
            <p>Indi bastante/Kulang ang training sang healthcare workers (e.g., kinahanglan pa sang dugang nga training agud masunod ang quality standards sang pasilidad)</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
  - name: FACILITYHEADSURVEY_DICT.Q49_QUALITY_CHALL_O06
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>49. What are the major challenges to improving the quality of patient care in your local area? — Lack of patient awareness of UHC benefits</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Kakulangan sa kamalayan ng pasyente tungkol sa benepisyo ng UHC (hal. hindi alam ng pasyente na maaari silang makinabang sa libreng konsultasyon, piling gamot, at serbisyo sa laboratoryo)</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Kulang an kaaraman kan pasyente manungod sa benepisyo kan UHC (e.g., Warang kaaraman an pasyente na pwede palan magavail ki libreng konsultasyon asin mga selected na bulong asin mga iba laboratory services</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>49. What are the major challenges to improving the quality of patient care in your local area? — Lack of patient awareness of UHC benefits</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Kulang sa kahibalo ang mga pasyente bahin sa mga benepisyo sa UHC (e.g. mga pasyente wala kabalo nga pwede sila maka avail ug libre nga konsultasyon, mga pili nga tambal ug laboratory services)</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Kakulang hin kaaram han pasyente han mga benepisyo han UHC (e.g., diri maaram an mga pasyente nga makakapahimulos hira hin libre nga konsultasyon, ngan pinili nga mga medisina ngan mga serbisyo ha laboratoryo)</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          HIL: |
            <p>Kulang ang ihibalo sang pasyente parte sa benepisyo sang UHC (e.g., indi kabalo nga pwede sila makakuha sang libre nga consultation, bulong, kag laboratory services)</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
  - name: FACILITYHEADSURVEY_DICT.Q49_QUALITY_CHALL_O07
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>49. What are the major challenges to improving the quality of patient care in your local area? — Limited accessibility of public healthcare facilities</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Limitadong aksesibilidad ng mga pampublikong pasilidad sa kalusugan (hal. kakulangan sa transportasyon, hindi maginhawang lokasyon, o pisikal na hadlang na nagpapahirap sa pasyente)</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Limitadong access sa pasilidad kan public healthcare (e.g., kulang sa transportation options, incovenient location, asin physical barriers sagabal sa access sa pasyente.)</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>49. What are the major challenges to improving the quality of patient care in your local area? — Limited accessibility of public healthcare facilities</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Limitado ang accessibility sa public healthcare facilities (e.g. kulang sa transportasyon, dili convenient ang lokasyon, o pisikal nga mga babag nga nag-pugong sa pag-access para sa pasyente</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Limitado nga pag-agi han mga pasilidad han panlawas han pampubliko (pananglitan, kakulang hin mga kapilian hin transportasyon, diri kombenyente nga lokasyon, o pisikal nga mga ulang nga nakakaulang han pag-agi para han mga pasyente.)</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          HIL: |
            <p>Limitado ang access sa public healthcare facilities (e.g., kulang sa transportasyon, indi maayo ang lokasyon, ukon may physical barriers nga naga-upang sa pasyente)</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
  - name: FACILITYHEADSURVEY_DICT.Q49_QUALITY_CHALL_O08
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>49. What are the major challenges to improving the quality of patient care in your local area? — Infrastructure not conducive for patient care</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>mprastraktura na hindi angkop para sa pangangalaga ng pasyente (hal. walang ground floor, kakulangan sa mga silid, hindi sapat na pasilidad sa kalinisan, kawalan ng accessibility para sa wheelchair, atbp.)</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Imprastaktura kan pasilidad dae angay sa pagaalaga sa pasyente (e.g., wara ki ground flr, kakulangan kan mga kwarto, warang marhay na sanitation, kakulangan ki wheelchair, etc.)</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>49. What are the major challenges to improving the quality of patient care in your local area? — Infrastructure not conducive for patient care</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Ang imprastraktyur dili maayo alang sa patient care (e.g. walay ground floor, kulang sa mga rooms, dili igo ang sanitation facilities, kulang sa wheelchair accessibility, etc)</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Mga imprastraktura nga diri maupay para han pag-ataman han pasyente (e.g., waray salog ha ubos, kakulang hin mga kwarto, diri igo nga mga pasilidad ha kalimpyo, kakulang hin pag-agi han mga lingkuran nga de-kaliding, ngan iba pa)</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
          HIL: |
            <p>Indi maayo ang infrastructure para sa pag-atipan sang pasyente (e.g., wala ground floor, kulang sang kuwarto, indi maayo ang sanitation facilities, kulang sa wheelchair accessibility, etc.)</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING.</p>
