  - name: FACILITYHEADSURVEY_DICT.Q57_CAPITATION_AMT
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>57. Based on your knowledge, what is the capitation amount of the YAKAP/Konsulta package? (Capitation is the amount per year per registered patient for delivering the YAKAP/Konsulta package services.)</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>(Capitation is the amount per year per registered patient for delivering the YAKAP/Konsulta package services .)</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Base sa saimong kaaraman, ano an capitation amount kan YAKAP/Konsulta package? (Capitation ini an amount kada taon para sa pag rehistro kan pasyente para sa YAKAP/Konsulta package na mga serbisyo)</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Base sa imohang kahibalo, pila ang capitation amount sa YAKAP/Konsulta nga package services?</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Base sa imong kaugalingon nga kahibalo, unsa ang capitation amount sa YAKAP/Konsulta package (Capitation is the amount per year per registered patient for delivering the YAKAP/Konsulta package services.) (Capitation mao ang kantidad kada tuig kada pasyente alang sa paghatag sa mga serbisyo sa YAKAP/Konsulta package)</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Base han imo nahibabaroan, ano an capitation amount han putos han YAKAP/Konsulta? (An capitasyon amo an kantidad kada tuig kada rehistrado nga pasyente para han paghatag han YAKAP/Konsulta package services.)</p>
          HIL: |
            <p>Base sa imo ihibalo, pila ang capitation amount sang YAKAP/Konsulta package? (Ang capitation amo ang kantidad nga ginahatag kada tuig para sa kada narehistro nga pasyente agud mahatagan sang YAKAP/Konsulta nga serbisyo.)</p>
  - name: FACILITYHEADSURVEY_DICT.Q58_PERF_INDICATORS_O01
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>58. What are the performance indicators you need to meet to receive the second tranche payment? — Beneficiaries consulted a primary care doctor</p><p class="instruction">Performance indicators are the defined set of healthcare goods and services to be provided for each enrolled patient to receive the full capitation payment. DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THE ANSWER OPTIONS THAT THE RESPONDENT GIVES WITHOUT PROMPTING. RESPONDENT MAY NOT BE ALLOWED TO LOOK FOR REFERENCE PRIOR TO ANSWERING THIS QUESTION.</p>
          FIL: |
