          EN: |
            <p>108. Have you heard about the Guaranteed and Accessible Medications for Outpatient Treatment (GAMOT) package?</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Nakarinig ka na ba tungkol sa Guaranteed and Accessible Medications for Outpatient Treatment (GAMOT) package?</p>
          BCL: |
