          CEB: |
            <p>Ang mga pasyente dili moagi sa proseso sa pag-avail</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THAT APPLY.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>An mga pasyente diri nakadto ha proseso han pag-avail hini</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THAT APPLY.</p>
          HIL: |
            <p>Ang mga pasyente wala napasulod sa proseso sang pag-avail sini</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THAT APPLY.</p>
  - name: FACILITYHEADSURVEY_DICT.Q137_NBB_BARRIERS_O04
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>137. In your view, what are some of the barriers to implementing the no balance billing (NBB) policy? — Insufficient PhilHealth support value</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THAT APPLY.</p>
          FIL: |
