            <p>140. In your view, what are some of the barriers to implementing the "zero balance billing" policy? — Complying with prescribed allocation ratio (basic vs non-basic)</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THAT APPLY.</p>
          FIL: |
