  - name: FACILITYHEADSURVEY_DICT.Q140_ZBB_BARRIERS_O03
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>140. In your view, what are some of the barriers to implementing the "zero balance billing" policy? — Patients do not go through the process of availing it</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THAT APPLY.</p>
