  - name: FACILITYHEADSURVEY_DICT.Q161_REF_SATISFACTION
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>161. How would you rate your satisfaction with your current referral system?</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THAT APPLY.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Paano ninyo irarate ang inyong kasiyahan sa kasalukuyang referral system?</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THAT APPLY.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Paano nindo ire-rate an saindong satisfaction sa kasalukuyang referral system?</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THAT APPLY.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Paunsa nimo I-rate ang imohang satisfaction sa kasamtangang sistema sa inyohang referral?</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THAT APPLY.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Unsaon nimo pag grado sa katagbawan sa inyong kasamtangang sistema sa referral?</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THAT APPLY.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Ano an imo paghatag hin grado han imo katagbaw ha imo yana nga sistema han pagrefer?</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THAT APPLY.</p>
          HIL: |
            <p>Ano ang nahamut-an mo nga grado sang inyo referral system subong?</p><p class="instruction">READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THAT APPLY.</p>
  - name: FACILITYHEADSURVEY_DICT.Q162_NOT_SATISFIED_WHY_O01
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>162. Why are you not satisfied with the current referral system? — Facilities overcrowded / do not accept our patient referrals</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THAT APPLY.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Masikip/puno ang mga pasilidad at hindi tinatanggap ang aming mga referral ng pasyente</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THAT APPLY.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Siksikan na an mga pasilidad / sobra na sa kapasidad asin dae nag-aako kan referrals</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THAT APPLY.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>Ang mga pasilidad naghuot na kaayo / sobra na sa kapasidad ug dili na modawat sa among mga pasyente nga gi-refer</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THAT APPLY.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Puno na ang mga pasilidad ug dili na modawat sa among mga gi-refer nga pasyente</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THAT APPLY.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>Sobra ka puno/sobra an kapasidad han mga pasilidad ngan diri nakarawat han amon mga pasyente nga ginrefer</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THAT APPLY.</p>
          HIL: |
            <p>Magutok ukon sobra sa kapasidad kag wala nagabaton sang gina-refer nga pasyente ang pasilidad.</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THAT APPLY.</p>
  - name: FACILITYHEADSURVEY_DICT.Q162_NOT_SATISFIED_WHY_O02
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>162. Why are you not satisfied with the current referral system? — Referral process is slow</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THAT APPLY.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Mabagal ang proseso ng referral</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THAT APPLY.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Maluya an referral process</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THAT APPLY.</p>
          BIS: |
