          HIL: |
            <p>Mahinay ang proseso sang referral</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THAT APPLY.</p>
  - name: FACILITYHEADSURVEY_DICT.Q162_NOT_SATISFIED_WHY_O03
    conditions:
      - questionText:
          EN: |
            <p>162. Why are you not satisfied with the current referral system? — Poor coordination between facilities</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THAT APPLY.</p>
          FIL: |
            <p>Mahina ang koordinasyon sa pagitan ng aming pasilidad at ng mga pinapadalang pasilidad</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THAT APPLY.</p>
          BCL: |
            <p>Maluya an koordinasyon kan saindong pasilidad asin kan mga gin-referan</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THAT APPLY.</p>
          BIS: |
            <p>162. Why are you not satisfied with the current referral system? — Poor coordination between facilities</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THAT APPLY.</p>
          CEB: |
            <p>Dili maayo ang koordinasyon tali sa among pasilidad ug sa mga gi-referan nga pasilidad</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THAT APPLY.</p>
          WAR: |
            <p>May maluya nga koordinasyon ha butnga han aton pasilidad ngan mga ginrefer nga mga pasilidad</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THAT APPLY.</p>
          HIL: |
            <p>Indi maayo ang koordinasyon sa tunga sang pasilidad kag gina-referan nga pasilidad.</p><p class="instruction">DO NOT READ OPTIONS OUT LOUD. SELECT ALL THAT APPLY.</p>
